# -*- coding: utf-8 -*-

"""Detect PRC GLOBAL watermarks from Alt Diffusion images or zT tensors.

Design:
  - Keep the PRC official decode path, key/meta loading, zT direct mode, CSV output,
    and summary style as close as possible to the original PRC detector.
  - Replace only the SD-specific image -> zT inverse layer with an Alt Diffusion
    approximate inverse:
        image -> Alt VAE encode -> DDIMInverseScheduler -> approximate zT

Notes:
  - The Alt inverse here is approximate. It is not the official SD exact inversion API.
  - Safety checker is disabled by default because Alt experiments already showed it can
    black out images and break the image->zT->decode path.
"""

